{"tid":1719683,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"成版熱門都仇恨post","createTime":"2019-11-14T06:55:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T10:30:22.000Z","uid":50457,"like":219,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":101,"replies":[{"pid":"83feb9d2c6d1915c8e579449ff1f8ef376d40c0d","tid":1719683,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T06:55:24.000Z","msg":"乜殺晒班藍屍，黑社會，場運動就會贏架咩？<br />\n<br />\n個堆全部都係扯線公仔，根本無價值<br />\n<br />\n愈係嬲就愈要保持冷靜<br />\n<br />\n尋日同今日，咁多暴力藍屍，警黑勾結，南亞仔，你估真係咁啱得咁橋？<br />\n<br />\n中共一方面利用黑警牽制各大院校，另一方面放班鄉黑出嚟，正正就係想制造人民鬥人民的場面<br />\n<br />\n對上一次一樣係三罷日，8月5日，荃灣黑幫，北角福建幫，深水埗南亞幫，全部都係針對8.5三罷走出嚟。<br />\n<br />\n第二次喇，仲未學精？唔好成日意為自己Iron man 托世好唔好，出面仲有一堆小朋友跟大隊，你走得到的時候，佢哋走唔切。到時你就be water, 其他手足就中彈，被人斬，之後又集氣又剩。<br />\n<br />\n出鄉黑未休息一日半日囉，咪成日憤怒掩蓋理性，敵人出無責任的爛仔刀手，自己衝上前做咩姐？好威威？真係可以所有人全身而退？無人想手足受傷，甚至死亡，<span style=\"color: red;\">死係黑社會手上，一啲價值都無。</span><br />\n<br />\n仲有，火魔法就唔好亂用，尤其是商舖上面有住宅。呢個仆街政府，絕對夠膽死叫消防唔做嘢，等上面住的人活生生燒死，到時話你知而家所有&ldquo;不割蓆&rdquo;通通都會係癈話。<br />\n<br />\n一定唔會有人接受放火殺人，即使你原意純粹係燒舖，但如果真係咁間接有人死，絕對無人會保，呢個係良知底線。<br />\n<br />\n中共重視死物，香港人重視人命，如果同中共一樣做法，咁大家注定永遠唔會成功。<br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭有排打，想繼續行落去，一定要好小心，民意唔係永恆，隨時都會逆轉，唔可以比憤怒充昏頭腦。"},{"pid":"0c92c39a1c22f5acb4c55555795dcfe3fd3adae3","tid":1719683,"uid":82955,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T06:55:49.000Z","msg":"[文宣升級&mdash;要追上前線行動呀！]<br />\n解鎖新職業 &mdash; 郵差叔叔，速遞員！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1717313\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1717313</a><br />\n<br />\n唔好意思，手足，借個位，認同請幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n發生好多事，好多怨案，令我地好嬲好嬲。但文宣一定要做足做好，我地係為正義而戰，我地從來都唔係暴徒！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/arAivP6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FarAivP6.png&h=a9a1a627&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zSLZfgM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzSLZfgM.jpg&h=20bdb60e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3c51578f94d824decf81baca617f6eb3029c7197","tid":1719683,"uid":258598,"like":2,"dislike":30,"score":-28,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T06:56:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0e6cbd37a90c7b497c3072e4b4a2fa96a30a8298","tid":1719683,"uid":278228,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T07:00:25.000Z","msg":"可以保護手足，但係巿民打巿民就係正苦想見到既野<br />\n記得要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">搞就搞高官</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"616c411ae40d332506dd881b5db5694e72c0c1e0","tid":1719683,"uid":58317,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T07:05:50.000Z","msg":"Be water my friend<br />\n勿忘初心"},{"pid":"29b50ef671c6604194e70091e860ffc5015ba33b","tid":1719683,"uid":50457,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"3c51578f94d824decf81baca617f6eb3029c7197","tid":1719683,"uid":258598,"like":2,"dislike":30,"score":-28,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T06:56:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T07:06:41.000Z","msg":"五毛狗即刻出動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n過返discuss搵食喇"},{"pid":"f0f6a265dda72bc4c66396e6c8cd203e3d25424e","tid":1719683,"uid":196329,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"3c51578f94d824decf81baca617f6eb3029c7197","tid":1719683,"uid":258598,"like":2,"dislike":30,"score":-28,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T06:56:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T07:06:41.000Z","msg":"P牌仔引戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8af41d24b3d02d2eefdb554101c3395cd2c12c4","tid":1719683,"uid":273886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T07:07:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"018619ff6416acdf1c325b145b6220a89fa2f7f4","tid":1719683,"uid":263